1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:08,500
I've had enough. Piloting the Eva, being at NERV — I hate all of it.

2
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:15,500
Shinji Ikari is missing. He's not at home, school, or headquarters.

3
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:22,500
Deploy a search team. Check surveillance camera footage across all of Tokyo-3.

4
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Without a pilot, we won't be able to respond when the next Angel arrives.

5
00:00:33,500 --> 00:00:37,000
Proceed with arrangements for an alternate pilot. What is the status of Unit-00's pilot, Rei Ayanami?

6
00:00:40,500 --> 00:00:44,000
Ayanami is still recovering from severe injuries. I assess that combat deployment is impossible.

7
00:00:47,500 --> 00:00:51,000
Nobody needs me. Not Father. Not anyone.

8
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:58,000
It started raining. Where should I go? I have no place to return to.

9
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:05,000
I got on a train, thinking I'd go as far away as possible. But I didn't know which station to get off at.

10
00:01:08,500 --> 00:01:12,000
If I don't pilot it, someone else gets hurt. But I don't want to be hurt anymore.

11
00:01:15,500 --> 00:01:19,000
I want to run away, but there's nothing waiting wherever I run. In the end, this is the only place I have.

12
00:01:22,500 --> 00:01:26,000
Report from NERV Security. Shinji Ikari located on the outskirts of Tokyo-3.

13
00:01:29,500 --> 00:01:33,000
Shinji... you came back.

14
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:40,000
I'm home... though I'm not sure if I'm allowed to say that.

15
00:01:43,500 --> 00:01:47,000
Welcome home.

16
00:01:50,500 --> 00:01:54,000
I still don't know why I pilot the Eva. But for now, I want to be here.

17
00:01:57,500 --> 00:02:01,000
If you chose to stay of your own will, then that's enough.

18
00:02:04,500 --> 00:02:08,000
Shinji Ikari, returning to duty as pilot. Please begin preparations to reactivate Unit-01.

19
00:02:11,500 --> 00:02:15,000
Eva Unit-01, all systems nominal. Synchronization rate... it's higher than before.

20
00:02:18,500 --> 00:02:22,000
People can't live alone. But being with others is frightening too. Even so, you have no choice but to keep moving forward.
